Package dataStructuresImplemented

Class DataHolder

java.lang.Object
dataStructuresImplemented.DataHolder
public class DataHolder
extends java.lang.Object
This is the main class which contains the data while in runtime. The data is stored in hash maps. The only thing that is not stored here is the friends relationships. They are stored in Person class, inside one of their attributes. This class is a singleton.
Author:
Borja Moralejo Tobajas and Imanol Mara√±a Hurtado
